{"tid":1262552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔睇議事論事都唔知612立法會保安唔俾議員入去","createTime":"2019-06-27T17:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T06:06:15.000Z","uid":26418,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37979547f5e0b839fc5c02dd7466b6494ec06d39","tid":1262552,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"大家一定要睇多啲港台節目<br />\n無論係鏗鏘集 視點31 議事論事 頭條新聞<br />\n定係每晚十點半嘅新聞天地<br />\n算係好盡詳同中立講每件事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uRw8ex-H6gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuRw8ex-H6gg&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPGZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=2c6a124d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uRw8ex-H6gg</a><br />\n<br />\n6:13開始講<br />\n立法會發出左黃色警示<br />\n但警方由只係做佈防工作 <br />\n變左帶示威者入房審問<br />\n啲保安仲要趕議員出房<br />\n<br />\n8:26開始講<br />\n立法會封哂所有入口<br />\n唔俾議員入立法會<br />\n話基於「安全理由」<br />\n唔通立法會出面好安全？又催淚彈又橡膠子彈<br />\n同埋阻止議員入去立法會開會 算唔算違反權力及特權條例？<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075c08733a52caa4bc953121761712cb333f7bad","tid":1262552,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:49:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8196adca37a8f7f01ea93a36e817bda3b7b4a51a","tid":1262552,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:50:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef23863390ca826e1dfc345164e44e0bb38ad7e","tid":1262552,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T17:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800451dbfcea0e015cdd3e3199703e1728949f45","tid":1262552,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"